com.jalios.jcms.archive

Class ArchivedPublication

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jalios.jcms.archive.ArchivedPublication
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DBData, JcmsConstants, JaliosConstants, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ArchivedPublication>

    public class ArchivedPublication
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<ArchivedPublication>, DBData, JcmsConstants
    This class represents an archived Publication in memory, used to keep track of authors, rights, category, workspace of archived publication
